                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; a few lines in the incipit page of
                           Text I, alternating with black lines; two initial lines of each section
                           of the text; elements of punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic
                           numerals; some words like kǝfl (e.g., fols. 7vc, 46rb, 142rb), fǝkkāre
                           (e.g., fols. 140vb, 141ra, 142vc), rabǝʿ (e.g., fols. 141vb, 142rc,
                           144ra).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
